description: Max iter = 1000. Performs 25 mc runs at integer undersampling point in the grid of lower-width 0.1 and upper width 0.2 around predicted undersampling point, with blocksoft denoiser. Sparsity varies in [0.02, ..., 0.98] with increment 0.02. No. of rows varies in [100, 200] and no. of columns is [3, 5, 10, 20]. cov(resid) used to estimate the noise covariance at each iteration instead of resid.T * resid/n.
